content: Anybody know which room the lab is in today?
Sometimes I just feel like a slice of bread.
If Im not back in five minutes, just wait longer.
Why do they call it rush hour when nothing moves?
I prefer not to think before speaking. I like being as surprised as everyone else by what comes out of my mouth.
Woke up today. It was terrible.
The worst part of online shopping is having to get up and get your credit card from your wallet.
Money cannot buy health, but I'd settle for a diamond-studded wheelchair.
